    <text type="letter">
        <body>
            <opener>
                <dateline>
                    <name type="place">431 Stevens Street</name>
                    <name type="place">Camden, New Jersey</name>
                    <date when="1880-01-14"><choice><abbr>Jan</abbr><expan>January</expan></choice> 14 '80</date>
                </dateline>
            </opener>
            
            <p>After I left you<ptr target="med.00635_n1"/> I went to Colorado, &#38; there &#38; in Missouri have spent the time since&#8212;came back here about a week ago&#8212;I sent you a little Volume&#8212;also two little pictures&#8212;You take the one you prefer &#38; give the other to Linton&#8212;Send me word if they come safe. I am all right in health.</p>

            <closer>
                <signed rend="right">Walt Whitman</signed>
            </closer>
        </body>
